Description: Replication of Chari, Christiano and Kehoe (1994) Table 2 using the approach from Benigno and Woodford
    (2005) to solve the Ramsey optimal taxation problem. The code is structured in a way that allows for full replication of
    Table 5 in BW05, which matches CCK94 results.
